       IDENTIFICATION   DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.      prog.
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
           DISPLAY FUNCTION LENGTH ("abcd" & "xyz")
           END-DISPLAY
           DISPLAY FUNCTION BYTE-LENGTH ("abcd" & "xyz")
           END-DISPLAY
           DISPLAY FUNCTION LENGTH ("abcd" "xyz")
           END-DISPLAY
           DISPLAY FUNCTION LENGTH ("abcd" & "xyz" PHYSICAL)
